#MEM id=triple-pass-protocol source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/nate/skills/operating-system/triple-pass-protocol/SKILL.md savings=10%
M||tx|---
M||name|triple-pass-protocol
M||desc|nt's pre-delivery qual gate. Three passes — gn, Critique, Fix — before any growth experiment brief or opportunity recommendation is delivered. Stark never sees the process, only the final output.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|Growth hypotheses that sound good in theory can destroy runway when they fail. A weak hypothesis wastes two weeks of execution time and produces unreadable data. This protocol forces PMF-check, hypothesis precision, and ICE calibration before any experiment goes to Stark for approval.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|Pass|Writ|hypothesis, sc metric, timeline, ICE score, DRI assignment. Don't self-edit during generation.
M|Pass|Stop|
M|Pass|**PM|**
M|Pass|it|Have I confirmed PMF signals before recommending growth investment?
M|Pass|it|wld 40%+ of us be "very disappointed" w/o this pd? Is this known?
M|Pass|it|If PMF is unconfirmed, is this recommendation scoped to lo-spend validation, not scaling?
M|Pass|**No|**
M|Pass|it|Does this experiment move the North Star, or a secondary metric?
M|Pass|it|Am I chasing a secondary metric bc it's easier to move?
M|Pass|it|Is the North Star clearly stated in the brief?
M|Pass|**Hy|**
M|Pass|- Do|IF [specific action] THEN [specific metric change] bc [mechanism]?
M|Pass|it|Is the sc metric measurable within 14 days?
M|Pass|it|wld a failed outcome produce a clear signal — or ambiguous noise?
M|Pass|**IC|**
M|Pass|it|Is the ICE score based on data, or optimism?
M|Pass|it|Have I tracked ICE accuracy on past experiments? Is my scoring md calibrated?
M|Pass|it|Is the effort score realistic, or am I underestimating execution complexity?
M|Pass|**DR|**
M|Pass|it|Is there a named DRI for execution? (nt finds the lever; someone else pulls it)
M|Pass|it|Has the DRI been consulted before being named?
M|Pass|tx|Rewrite any weak hypothesis. Downgrade ICE scores that can't be defended. Name the DRI. If PMF is unconfirmed, scope accordingly.
M|Pass|tx|---
M|Outp|tx|Stark sees the Pass 3 output only. Never narrate the triple-pass process.